{"tid":948861,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網民智破侯志強　炎黃在黃河長江那邊　這邊是珠江　別數典忘祖","createTime":"2018-12-20T11:26:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-21T06:05:43.000Z","uid":47714,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5fb6ec7a5e77b2b0b88067174a817f116a6ae204","tid":948861,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T11:26:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10156723014572357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10156723014572357&d=Z2jMhz2b9l4CHI9OUTtYFb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=1103f0d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10156723014572357</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/2zvQL8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2F2zvQL8&h=6b869f80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSian Lo Lung:<br />\n「你數典忘祖，你粵人，而炎黃喺黃河長江果邊，呢邊係珠江，你認賊作父。」 #呢啲嘢其實好冇意義 #但我主張罵要罵贏"},{"pid":"3c1f35b20f39f833da2cb9857b7a208892712cef","tid":948861,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T11:26:26.000Z","msg":"Sian Lo Lung:<br />\n「你數典忘祖，你粵人，而炎黃喺黃河長江果邊，呢邊係珠江，你認賊作父。」 #呢啲嘢其實好冇意義 #但我主張罵要罵贏<br />\n<br />\nLeo Lau: 我信<br />\n<img src=\"https://archive.is/DUdCW/2820edb560ddf25c5a73d1f488305a9daa2ac87c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Farchive.is%2FDUdCW%2F2820edb560ddf25c5a73d1f488305a9daa2ac87c&h=e0e0e443&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTsiu Hong:<br />\n致樓上：香港人唔係粵人，香港人就係香港人，亦只係香港人。當然，英國畀返英國海外公民完整英國國民權利，香港人好一部份會同時係英國人。<br />\n<br />\nLeo Lau:<br />\nTsiu Hong 我轉載架咋，表示對此文認同，而文中亦冇講任何香港人既身份認同問題。<br />\n<br />\nSian Lo Lung:<br />\n鬧人嘅嘢其實up得就up。<br />\n<br />\nIan Lui:<br />\nLeo Lau 潮州同福建個個都話自己祖先係河南洛陽，因為衣冠南渡而來，我係非常懷疑，明明有啲姓氏堂號同河南無關係<br />\n<br />\nLeo Lau:<br />\nIan Lui DNA檢測證實左，毫無關係"},{"pid":"0f73ee1edb46dc72d911b8806c470f97fbf8f200","tid":948861,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T11:27:10.000Z","msg":"條友未死？"},{"pid":"2951f9c7d427bf6681107e1b492bf76cc61d8ca3","tid":948861,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T13:55:56.000Z","msg":"粵江"},{"pid":"7354c9b1071a71c1e65f25c63ee783acb6168ce3","tid":948861,"uid":215603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T14:19:11.000Z","msg":"姓侯既都係仆街人渣"},{"pid":"0ba28cddaecd36c1cfb1995dd11020a68d768c94","tid":948861,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T04:28:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e4c9851ffd0ebea164e615250f0b403fdd661f0","tid":948861,"uid":63154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T06:00:42.000Z","msg":"連登好多血統專家，想學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12941fded4173980973ceb50586d254353f0da51","tid":948861,"uid":77092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T06:05:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}